  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      This study evaluated optimal macrophage diagnosis algorithm through comparative analysis
      between coronary artery, OCT image, and IVUS, and improve a diagnosis rate of vulnerable
      coronary plaque accompanied with macrophage infiltration.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
